SUMMARY:

 The proposed information collection requirements described below have been submitted to the Office of Management
and Budget (OMB) for expedited clearance under 5 CFR 1320.18. The Agency is soliciting public comments on the subject
submission. This action is necessary in order for the Agency to promulgate a new regulation to administer the Rural
Technology Development Grants (RTDG) program as required by legislation. Fiscal year (FY) 1994 appropriation contained
