Date: 23 May 1994, Expires: 31 December 1999.
Subject: Expiration of Geographic Jurisdictional Determinations.
1. Regulatory Guidance Letter (RGL) 90-6, Subject: ``Expiration Dates for Wetlands Jurisdictional Delineations''
is extended until 31 December 1999, subject to the following revisions.
2. This guidance should be applied to all jurisdictional determinations for all waters of the United States made pursuant
to Section 10 of the Rivers and Harbors Act of 1899, Section 404 of the Clean Water Act, and Section 103 of the Marine Protection
Research and Sanctuaries Act of 1972.
