Delineation of Wetlands for Purposes of Section 404 of the Clean Water Act and Subtitle B of the Food Security Act, all
U.S. Army Corps of Engineers geographic jurisdictional determinations shall be in writing and normally remain valid
for a period of five years. The Corps letter (see paragraph 4.(d) of RGL 90-6) should include a statement that
